        <updating/>
        <source>setForCreate(_proxy :CM_OwnershipChange)updating;
/*

Purpose:			

Parameters:			

Return Value:		

Date		Who		Reason
31 May 2023 navtnr20	TFS CR 58507	Task 58209: Jade - TRX CM_OwnershipChange

*/

